reviewText: Very useful, and real approach on how to get a consulting job.
Was a good introduction and provided a lot of valuable insight to the interview process
Well structured, clear topics and messages delivered. Amazing tips and tricks for networking, getting the next opportunity, landing that job/promotion!
Fantastic Course, have fallen in love with management consulting because of you sir!
I enjoyed learning with Prof. John Kim; he makes learning fun.

Exccllent Course for anyone with aspiratons to enter the world of consulancy. The course provides you great overview, insights of the craft and the preparatory tools and techniques needed to have a great shot at consultancy.
This is a great course for beginners to take to explore more about management consulting.

I took this course leading up to my first ever case interview.  While I could not fit every detail of my career into the short time frame (30min behavior/ 30min Case), topics from this course helped me make sure the things I spoke about were relevant to what skills they look for, showed my genuine interest in their company over others, as well as taking time to sound thoughtful and logical.  Above all, this course continues to support my growing interest in consulting.

The course is extremely engaging  and well structured. It doesn't feel long and laboured and that is absolutely awesome. John speaks well, explains perfectly and paces the work just right. Congratulations on an awesome course.
Excellent information presented in a timely and well instructed manner.
Really liked the content and how all the things matter to a college student, an employee and an entrepreneur.
